Balika ne janm lete hi boli ki Bharat mein jo corona virus sankraman phaila hua hai uske bachav ke liye Bharat ke pratyek nagrik ko apne daayein pair ke angothe par haldi ka lep (mehendi ki tarah) lagana hai. Isse corona ka sankraman samapt ho jayega. Sabhi nagrik suksham raheinge. Yeh kehkar balika ki usi samay mrityu ho gayi. Is dekhkar aspatal ke doctor bhi ashcharyachakit ho gaye. Atah aapse nivedan hai ki aap bhi tatkal is tarah ka lep apne daayein pair ke angothe par lagakar corona virus sankraman se apna aur apne parivaar ka jeevan bachayein. Yeh fake news nahi hai sachai ghatna hai.
